/bash.html.title: Bash
/bash.html.content:
• edit variable loop persist outside
    don’t use pipes those cause subshells:

    counter=0
    while read parameter variable">r line

     variable">((counter+1))
    done operator"><<< string">"${multilinething}
    echo "count: variable">${counter}"
  • set terminal title current running command ~/bashrc

    ###########################################################################
    # begin set #

    case environment constant">$term    " keyword">
    xterm*|rxvt*)
     variable">prompt_command'echo ne "\033]0;${user}@${hostname}: ${pwd}\007"'

     show currently title:
     http://wwwdavidpashleycom/articles/xtermtitleswithbashhtml
     functionname function">show_command_in_title_bar({
     variable">$bash_command" keyword">
     *\033]0*
     most likely execution $prompt_command

    docker operator">| function">grep operator"><search> function">awk string">'{print $1 ":" $2}' function">xargs rmi

    >/v2/<image>/tags/list jq string">'tags | reverse'
